		<control>gamepad</control>
	</supports>

	<description>
		<p>
			MPRIS Timer is really keyboard friendly! It should be quite intuitive. Use navigation (arrows, tab, shift+tab) or start inputting numbers right away. 
			Use either as a GUI app or as a CLI tool: see `mpris-timer -help`.
		</p>
	</description>

